Program: The Documentary
Title: Mumbai Mirror
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3csz3x2
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 17 Apr 2019
As the 2019 Indian election campaign kicks off, BBC World Service follows journalists from the daily Mumbai Mirror newspaper to get under the skin of the stories that matter to Mumbaikers. From daily editorial meetings to exclusive investigations this ‘fly-on-the-wall’ radio documentary offers insight into how a newspaper covers the life and news of India’s largest city. Produced by Nina Robinson and Rumella Dasgupta. Image: Bundles of the Mumbai Mirror newspaper (Credit: Nina Robinson/BBC) Show less